snippet.title: Space Raiders in Space! Launch trailer
snippet.description:
Join our discord for beta access!  https://discord.gg/MWDDnEp

Space Raiders in Space is a comic-themed squad management game where the player is tasked with keeping a group of opinionated raiders alive amidst an alien invasion of epic B-movie proportions.
